</p>
			</div>
		</div></li>
</ul>
<ul class="gallery mw-gallery-packed">
	<li class='gallerycaption'>Cascade Transition Exponent</li>
		<li class="gallerybox" style="width: 630px"><div style="width: 630px">
			<div class="thumb" style="width: 628px;"><div style="margin:0px auto;"><a href="/File:3TransitionHard.png" class="image"><img alt="" src="https://d26ilriwvtzlb.cloudfront.net/8/8a/3TransitionHard.png" width="628" height="300" /></a></div></div>
