</p>
			</div>
		</div></li>
</ul>
<p><b>Shadow Distance Fadeout Fraction</b>:  This controls the how the shadows fade out at distances. Higher values will fade the shadow out whereas lower values will leave a darker shadow at distances.
</p>
<ul class="gallery mw-gallery-packed">
	<li class='gallerycaption'>Shadow Distance Fadeout Fraction</li>
		<li class="gallerybox" style="width: 361.33333333333px"><div style="width: 361.33333333333px">
